  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The following WWDC videos provide additional information about HTTP Live Streaming.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "identifier": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2013/608/",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ":",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "AVFoundation automatically selects appropriate audio and subtitle tracks in your",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "media. Learn how media selection works and find out how to author media with accessibility",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "features like subtitles and closed captions. Go beyond the basics to use AVFoundation",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "for customizing subtitle appearance and presentation.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "identifier": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2015/502/",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ":",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "FairPlay streaming provides industrial-grade protection for audio and video content.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Learn how to implement and deploy FairPlay streaming to protect content when using",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "HTTP Live Streaming.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "identifier": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2016/510/",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ":",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "HTTP Live Streaming enables the reliable delivery of media content over a wide variety",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "of network conditions. Learn best practices in HLS authoring, see how to verify your",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "streams using the HTTP Live Streaming tools, and apply the results to improve the",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "performance of your streams.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "identifier": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2016/504/",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ":",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "HTTP Live Streaming offers a reliable media playback experiences over a wide variety",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "of network conditions. Join us to learn how to deliver offline playback using the",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "same media assets you already host for online playback. See new additions to the",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "HLS protocol, such as support for fragmented MP4 and in-playlist metadata.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "identifier": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2017/515/",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ":",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "HTTP Live Streaming (HLS) reliably delivers video to audiences around the world.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Key to this reliability is a comprehensive set of tools to help you author, deliver,",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "and validate the HLS streams you create. See whatâ€™s new in these tools, learn the",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "latest authoring recommendations, and how they apply to advances in HLS such as support",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "for HEVC and IMSC1.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "identifier": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2017/514/",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ":",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "HTTP Live Streaming (HLS) reliably delivers media content across a variety of network",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "and bandwidth conditions. However, there are many factors that can impact stream",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "delivery, such as server or encoder failures, caching issues, or network dropouts.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Learn the best-practice behaviors that your servers should adopt to maximize reliability,",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "and gain a practical understanding of the errors your app may encounter and how to",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "handle them.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "identifier": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2017/504/",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ":",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "HTTP Live Streaming allows you to stream live and on-demand content to global audiences.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Learn about great new features and enhancements to HTTP Live Streaming. Highlights",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "include support for HEVC, playlist metavariables, IMSC1 subtitles, and synchronized",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "playback of multiple streams. Discover how to simplify your FairPlay key handling",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "with the new AVContentKeySession API, and take advantage of enhancements to offline",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "HLS playback.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
